@Stewie G


The game just seems boring.  The mechanics aren't really interesting, and you have no idea what to do.  You just wander around interacting with stuff.  It's not the worst game ever made, but it does completely fail to grab your attention.


I guess it's not a terrible game if you like RPG's.  But there are so many good games on the SNES, I don't see why anyone would want to play Drakkhen over something else.
